no_permission.title: Insufficient Permissions!
no_permission.description: You need the `__permission__` permission or the `__node__` permission node in order to execute this command.

invalid_target.title: Invalid target!
invalid_target.description: Please specify a valid Role or User.

too_long.title: Prefix too long!
too_long.description: The prefix can be a maximum of 5 characters long.

reset.description: Resets the prefix to the default. (`__prefix__`)

toggle.description: Toggles the default (`__prefix__`) prefix. (Only works if you have set a custom prefix)

not_allowed.title: Not allowed to disable!
not_allowed.description: You first have to set a custom prefix in order to disable the default prefix.

language.description: Allows you to change the language of the bot.

unknown.title: Unknown language!
unknown.description:
The language __language__ is currently not supported. You can contribute to supported languages [here](https://app.phrase.com/accounts/michael-rittmeister/projects/votebot/dashboard).
  Currently supported: __supportedLanguages__

status.description: Allows you to change the bots status.

help.description: Shows a list containing all available commands.

not_found.title: Command not found!
not_found.description: I couldn't find a command with that name

info.title: Command-Help
info.description:
This is a list of all commands,
            | in order to learn more about a specific command run `v!help [command]`
